WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:04.366
Sorry.

2
00:00:04.933 --> 00:00:07.300
If I had known your true identity earlier

3
00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:10.366
Now there's no need to find out who's right and who's wrong.

4
00:00:10.900 --> 00:00:13.833
All I want is for us to be okay

5
00:00:14.066 --> 00:00:15.266
Child safe

6
00:00:15.566 --> 00:00:17.233
I'm content

7
00:00:17.533 --> 00:00:20.166
But what needs to be cleaned up has to be cleaned up

8
00:00:21.133 --> 00:00:22.900
What about my mom and Yun Xuewei?

9
00:00:22.933 --> 00:00:24.400
I'm all locked up

10
00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:25.700
How do you want to deal with it?

11
00:00:26.533 --> 00:00:27.433
My mom

12
00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:29.266
Just let her go

13
00:00:29.866 --> 00:00:33.233
After all, I still have to repay her for her upbringing

14
00:00:34.566 --> 00:00:35.766
As for the company

15
00:00:36.100 --> 00:00:37.433
Also let go

16
00:00:37.900 --> 00:00:39.366
That's my dad's work

17
00:00:40.500 --> 00:00:42.000
What about Yun Xuegui?

18
00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:44.233
The key is

19
00:00:44.933 --> 00:00:47.566
I owe my parents, not him

20
00:00:47.900 --> 00:00:50.266
He will pay for his actions

21
00:00:50.933 --> 00:00:53.066
Ok it's up to you

22
00:00:53.766 --> 00:00:55.166
And Mrs. Gu

23
00:00:55.266 --> 00:00:56.800
I don't blame him though

24
00:00:56.866 --> 00:00:59.100
But I don't want to see him anytime soon.

25
00:00:59.100 --> 00:01:00.266
And Mr. Shen

26
00:01:00.766 --> 00:01:02.766
If he hadn't arrived in time

27
00:01:03.933 --> 00:01:06.600
I'm doomed.

28
00:01:06.866 --> 00:01:08.700
No problem, don't worry.

29
00:01:08.733 --> 00:01:10.933
I will resume and review the cooperation.

30
00:01:10.933 --> 00:01:12.366
And the future will give him

31
00:01:12.366 --> 00:01:14.100
Three invaluable projects

32
00:01:14.466 --> 00:01:16.666
Ting Chuan, you are so nice.

33
00:01:30.066 --> 00:01:31.566
I couldn't take care of you before

34
00:01:31.566 --> 00:01:34.100
I will be a qualified husband in the future

35
00:01:34.100 --> 00:01:35.966
And give you a happy home

36
00:01:36.266 --> 00:01:38.433
Will you marry me again?

37
00:01:39.100 --> 00:01:39.900
OK

